  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Unleash your inner speed demon with Need for Speed Nitro for the Nintendo DS. This high-energy racing game delivers fast-paced, arcade-style action, letting you dominate the streets with style and speed.\n\nChoose from a wide selection of licensed cars from top manufacturers and customize them with an array of performance upgrades and visual modifications to create your ultimate racing machine. Race through vibrant and dynamic environments inspired by real-world locations, each filled with shortcuts and hidden paths that provide strategic advantages.\n\nTake on challenging AI opponents in various game modes, including Circuit, Elimination, and Drift. Master the art of drifting and nitro boosts to leave your rivals in the dust and achieve victory. The intuitive controls and responsive touch screen interface make car handling smooth and enjoyable.\n\nCompete with friends in local multiplayer races via DS Download Play, and show off your racing skills and custom rides. With its colorful graphics, pulse-pounding soundtrack, and exhilarating gameplay, Need for Speed Nitro for the Nintendo DS offers a thrilling racing experience that you can take anywhere.\n\nGet ready to rev your engines and burn rubber in a race to the finish line. Speed, style, and adrenaline await you in Need for Speed Nitro!",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
